						               													<description>Intelli Wars is a Strategic level Science-Fiction themed space wargame where you manage fleets of spaceships and spend available resources to attack and conquer your opponent&amp;rsquo;s star systems by deciding when to commit your forces, where they must go and with what support while repairing, refitting and bringing in reinforcements.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is a 2 player, competitive, turn based, card driven, board-wargame. This is a science-fiction war setting between two space empires. The map is a blank hex grid to allow for various scenarios and thus increase replay value. Players are in the role of fleet commanders in charge of a theater of war with a God&amp;rsquo;s eye point of view. The scope is that of a campaign operation; events are just part of the wider war.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A unit represents a fleet of spaceships and while the time scale is abstract a turn is meant to represent anywhere from a few weeks to a couple of months. To win you must achieve the scenario's victory point level.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game in its current format is print &amp;amp; play and files are provided in this page for downloading components and rules in electronic format for printing and assembling.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
